The,Bitport,API,allows,developers,to,create,torrent,related,extensions,and,plugins,The,Bitport,platform,is,used,to,download,torrents,to,the,cloud,and,play,them,online,All,the,work,is,done,by,Bitport,s,servers,so,the,user,s,IP,address,is,kept,secure,Also,torrents,can,be,accessed,anywhere,and,big,torrents,are,downloaded,faster